
<sellerabr>CHESAPEAKE</sellerabr> {<sellercode>CSK</sellercode>} SEEKS TO SELL UNIT
    WEST POINT, Va., April 7 - <seller>Chesapeake Corp</seller> said it has
retained Salomon Inc {SB} to help it sell <acquired>Plainwell Paper Co
Inc</acquired>, a maker of <acqbus>premium coated and uncoated printing papers and
technical specialty papers</acqbus> with a capacity of 85,000 short tons
a year.
    The company said it has decided to sell <acqabr>Plainwell</acqabr> in ordfer
to focus on the production of kraft and tissue products,
containers and treated wood products.
